text.section:
The Customer Council shall:
review the products and services of Maryland Correctional Enterprises;
advise the Chief Executive Officer on quality, availability, style, design, delivery, scheduling, and pricing;
recommend new products and services;
annually review the catalog of Maryland Correctional Enterprises products and recommend changes to improve the catalog;
recommend sales, marketing, and customer satisfaction initiatives;
annually review the Maryland Correctional Enterprises business plan; and
serve as a forum for raising and discussing issues related to any product or service offered by Maryland Correctional Enterprises.
